arell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/quincy-jones">昆西·琼斯（</a> <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janelle-monae">JanelleMonáe</a> ）致敬。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/prince-the-clash-and-frankie-valli-among-those-honoured-at-grammys-special-merit-awards-3833798"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）成为当晚最大的赢家，获得了五个奖项，包括年度纪录和年度最佳歌曲“不喜欢我们”。他还带回了格莱美奖，以获得最佳说唱表演和最佳说唱歌曲“ Not Like Us”，后者还赢得了最佳音乐录影带。 </p></div></div><figure id="attachment_3817240" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3817240" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3817240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kendrick-Lamar-@-2000-x-1270-Michael-Blackshire-_-Los-Angeles-Times-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）在音乐视频拍摄的“不喜欢我们”中拍摄。图片来源：Michael Blackshire / Los Angeles Times通过Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kendrick-Lamar-@-2000-x-1270-Michael-Blackshire-_-Los-Angeles-Times-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kendrick-Lamar-@-2000-x-1270-Michael-Blackshire-_-Los-Angeles-Times-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kendrick-Lamar-@-2000-x-1270-Michael-Blackshire-_-Los-Angeles-Times-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kendrick-Lamar-@-2000-x-1270-Michael-Blackshire-_-Los-Angeles-Times-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kendrick-Lamar-@-2000-x-1270-Michael-Blackshire-_-Los-Ange