ity Music Featuring Chandler Moore – In the Name of Jesus<br /> Maverick City Music, Naomi Raine &amp; Chandler Moore Featuring Tasha Cobbs Leonard – In the Room</p><p><strong>最佳福音专辑</strong><br /><strong>CeCe Winans – More Than This – WINNER</strong><br /> Karen Clark Sheard – Still Karen<br /> Kirk Franklin – Father&#39;s Day<br /> Melvin Crispell III – Covered Vol. 1<br /> Ricky Dillard – Choirmaster II (Live)</p><p><strong>最佳当代基督教音乐专辑</strong><br />Brandon Lake – Coat of Many Colors<br /> <strong>Doe – Heart of a Human – WINNER</strong><br /> Elevation Worship – When Wind Meets Fire<br /> Forrest Frank – Child of God<br /> Maverick City Music, Chandler Moore &amp; Naomi Raine – The Maverick Way Complete</p><p><strong>最佳根福音专辑</strong><br />Authentic Unlimited – The Gospel Sessions, Vol. 2<br /> <strong>Cory Henry – Church – WINNER</strong><br /> The Harlem Gospel Travelers – Rhapsody<br /> Mark D. Conklin – The Gospel According to Mark<br /> The Nelons – Loving You </p><figure id="attachment_3824908" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3824908" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3824908" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3824908" class="wp-caption-text"> doechii。 Credit: Rebecca Sapp/Getty Images for The Recording Academy</figcaption>