y to request a ticket return for each day the forecast is 90 degrees or higher.”</p><p> Hinterland 2025 will run from August 1 to 3 in Saint Charles, Iowa and will be headlined by <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tyler-the-creator">Tyler, The Creator</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kacey-musgraves">Kacey Musgraves</a> , with additional sets from <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/clairo">Clairo</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bleachers">Bleachers</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/remi-wolf">Remi Wolf</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/royel-otis">Royel Otis</a> and Wyatt Flores among others.</p><p> “If on 29 July at 10am CT, the weather.gov forecast for 1, 2 or 3 August has a true temperature of 90 degrees or higher for the 50240 zip code, ticket purchasers will have the option to request a return of their festival admission ticket for that day,” the festival added.</p><p> “Return requests are only available for the day/s the forecast is 90° or higher. Three-day ticket holders can request a return for specific day/s at a rate of 1/3 of the total three-day ticket price.”</p><p> Last year&#39;s Hinterland was headlined by <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vampire-weekend">Vampire Weekend</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ethel-cain">Ethel Cain</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-kahan">Noah Kahan</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hozier">Hozier</a> . <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noah-kahan-throws-support-behind-hinterland-co-headliner-im-really-here-for-chappell-roan-3780840">Kahan was seen on site enjoying Chappell Roan&#39;s set at the festival</a> from the side of stage. “I might be headlining but I&#39;m really here for Chappell Roan,” he quipped.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/us-festival-hinterland-offers-refunds-for-extremely-hot-days-3833848">US festival Hinterland offers ref